---
title: Tuscan-Inspired Bean Pasta with Chili Flakes and Lemon Zest
description: The cannellini bean, an Italian favourite, is made for pasta with its creamy, fluffy interior! Chili flakes, garlic, spinach and roasted tomatoes fill every other nook and cranny of this Tuscan-inspired pasta dish.
